      <div id="main-content">
        <p> Derrick Rose was drafted in 2008 by the Chicago Bulls and was named MVP in 2011.
          He was a revolutionary point guard who had a style and athleticism never seen before.
          This was all until he injured himself multiple times within the next year of his MVP award.
         After this Derrick Rose has never been the same and I am just hoping for the day when he comes back to his vintage self.</p>
       </div>
